**SCP-5489：**我，尼克松
**作者：**[[*user Dr Phil McClaw]]，一只甲壳纲动物
⚠️ **内容警告:** 本文不包含任何的敏感内容 :)
]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:image-features-source |hover-enlarge=--]
|enlarge-amount=3
|speed=500
|float=true
|align=right
|width=400px
|url=http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/scp-5489/scp-nixon-elvis.png
|add-caption=true
